@startuml
title CV Tajuk Revenue Cycle System - Activity Diagram

|Sales|
start
:Maintain Customer and Product data;
:Create a new transaction;

if (Is this a Pre Order?) then (Yes)
  |System|
  :Generate the Sales Order ID\nand PO ID;
  |Sales|
  :Enter required date and\nupload the PO document;
else (No)
  |System|
  :Generate the Sales Order ID;
endif

|Sales|
:Select the customer and products;
:Edit Base Price and enter optional\nMarkup or Discount;

|System|
:Calculate Unit Price and total;
:Validate and save the transaction;

if (Is this a Pre Order?) then (Yes)
  :Send the required-date reminder;
endif

:Evaluate customer payment risk;

if (Is Manager approval required?) then (Yes)
  |Manager|
  :Review the transaction;
  if (Is the transaction approved?) then (Yes)
    :Approve the transaction;
  else (No)
    :Reject the transaction;
    stop
  endif
endif

|Admin|
:Generate the Invoice;

|System|
:Create the Receivable;

if (Is the payment term Debit?) then (Yes)
  |Admin|
  :Record the payment;
else (No)
  |System|
  :Schedule the billing follow-up;
  |Sales|
  :Perform the billing follow-up;
  |Admin|
  :Record partial or full payment;
endif

|System|
:Update Invoice and Receivable status;

|Admin|
:Create the Surat Jalan;

|System|
:Generate printable Invoice and Surat Jalan\nwith transaction type and PO details;

|Customer|
:Receive the product and documents;
stop

@enduml
